<title>USA: Hayes says Western to assume KC Power's debt.</title>
<headline>Hayes says Western to assume KC Power's debt.</headline>
<dateline>KANSAS CITY, MO. 1997-02-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Western Resources will assume all of Kansas City Power and Light Co's debt as part of the two utilities' merger deal, Western Chairman and CEO John Hayes said in a teleconference Friday.</p>
<p>Hayes said Western would assume the debt, which KC Power's CEO Drue Jennings said totaled approximately $835 million.</p>
